00:05:47.480 --> 00:05:53.780
Unique and eternal your vision,
a truly rooted vigil excuse me,

00:05:53.780 --> 00:05:59.200
a truly rooted vigil your love
the strongest my teacher Riva.

00:05:59.200 --> 00:06:02.600
So, I absorb the sunset which
has lit before me a corner

00:06:02.600 --> 00:06:05.040
