and it is associated Jewish learning

00:07:15.300 --> 00:07:18.760
with a very pleasant experience.

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:22.550
Rivka new loss at a very
young age, her mother died

00:07:22.550 --> 00:07:26.080
when she was still a child,
her grandma stepped in.

00:07:26.080 --> 00:07:32.480
When the Nazis emptied Rivka's
town of Jews Rivka was 14.

00:07:32.480 --> 00:07:35.260
