00:14:02.470 --> 00:14:08.420
She met and married Shmuel
nicknamed Mula Ben-Hayim

00:14:08.420 --> 00:14:11.390
after the war in Belgrade.

00:14:11.390 --> 00:14:17.560
Mula ran the Belgrade station of
the organization known as Berihah,

00:14:17.560 --> 00:14:21.440
the Hebrew word for
flight or escape.

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:26.240
The members of this organization
